Package org.moeaframework.util.grammar

Utilities for representing, parsing and building grammars for use in Grammatical Evolution (GE).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
ContextFreeGrammar A context-free grammar.
Parser Parses simple context-free grammars in Backus-Naur form (BNF).
Production A context-free grammar production.
Rule A context-free grammar rule.
Symbol A context-free grammar symbol.
 

Exception Summary
GrammarException Exception indicating an error while parsing or processing grammars.
 

Package org.moeaframework.util.grammar Description

Utilities for representing, parsing and building grammars for use in Grammatical Evolution (GE).

References:

  1. Ryan, C., Collins, J.J., and O'Neill, M. "Grammatical Evolution: Evolving Programs for an Arbitrary Language." Lecture Notes in Computer Science, Proceedings of the First European Workshop on Genetic Programming, pp. 82-95, 1998.
